==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pleadings
<hw>Plead"ings</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <fld>(Law)</fld>
<def>The mutual pleas and replies of the plaintiff and defendant, or
written statements of the parties in support of their claims, proceeding
from the declaration of the plaintiff, until issue is joined, and the
question made to rest on some single point.</def>
<rj><au>Blackstone.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pleasance</ent>⟦br⟧
